<h3>Textbooks</h3>
<ul>
<li>Giacomo Bonanno, <a href="http://faculty.econ.ucdavis.edu/faculty/bonanno/PDF/GT_book.pdf"><em>Game Theory</em></a></li>
<li>Martin Robinson and Ariel Rubenstein, <a href="http://gametheory.tau.ac.il/arielDocs/"><em>A Course in Game Theory</em></a></li>
<li>Kevin Leyton-Brown and Yoav Shoham, <a href="http://www.morganclaypool.com/doi/abs/10.2200/S00108ED1V01Y200802AIM003"><em>Essentials of Game Theory</em></a></li>
</ul>
<p>Note that the second requires free registration, and the third requires to be logged into a UM Computer.</p>
